// src/components/CacheAndSWDemo.module.styl
// 定义变量
primary = #4361ee
secondary = #3a0ca3
success = #4cc9f0
warning = #f72585
light = #f8f9fa
dark = #212529
gray = #6c757d

// 组件样式
.container
  max-width: 1200px
  margin: 0 auto
  background: white
  border-radius: 12px
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)
  overflow: hidden

.header
  background: primary
  color: white
  padding: 2rem
  text-align: center

  h1
    font-size: 2.5rem
    margin-bottom: 1rem

.subtitle
  font-size: 1.2rem
  opacity: 0.9

.content
  padding: 2rem
  display: grid
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr
  gap: 2rem

  @media (max-width: 768px)
    grid-template-columns: 1fr

.card
  background: light
  border-radius: 10px
  padding: 1.5rem
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)

  h2
    color: primary
    margin-bottom: 1rem
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem
    border-bottom: 2px solid success

  h3
    color: secondary
    margin: 1.2rem 0 0.5rem

pre
  background: #2d2d2d
  color: #f8f8f2
  padding: 1rem
  border-radius: 5px
  overflow-x: auto
  margin: 1rem 0
  font-family: 'Consolas', monospace

code
  padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem
  border-radius: 3px
  font-family: 'Consolas', monospace

.metrics
  display: grid
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr)
  gap: 1rem
  margin-top: 2rem
  padding: 0 2rem

  @media (max-width: 992px)
    grid-template-columns: 1fr

.metricCard
  background: white
  padding: 1.5rem
  border-radius: 10px
  text-align: center
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)
  border-top: 4px solid

  &.lcp
    border-color: warning

  &.cls
    border-color: success

  &.inp
    border-color: primary

.metricValue
  font-size: 2rem
  font-weight: bold
  margin: 0.5rem 0

.metricLabel
  font-size: 1rem
  color: gray

.status
  display: inline-block
  padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem
  border-radius: 20px
  font-size: 0.9rem
  margin-top: 0.5rem

  &.good
    background: #e6f7ee
    color: #0a9955

  &.poor
    background: #fde8e8
    color: #e53e3e

.btn
  display: inline-block
  background: primary
  color: white
  padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem
  border-radius: 6px
  text-decoration: none
  font-weight: 600
  margin-top: 1rem
  transition: all 0.3s ease
  border: none
  cursor: pointer
  margin-right: 1rem

  &:hover
    background: secondary
    transform: translateY(-2px)

.footer
  text-align: center
  padding: 2rem
  color: gray
  font-size: 0.9rem

.cacheDemo
  margin-top: 1.5rem
  padding: 1rem
  background: #f8f9fa
  border-radius: 8px
  border-left: 4px solid primary

.demoControls
  display: flex
  gap: 1rem
  margin-top: 1rem
  flex-wrap: wrap

.demoResult
  margin-top: 1rem
  padding: 1rem
  background: #e9ecef
  border-radius: 6px
  min-height: 80px
  white-space: pre-line

ul
  padding-left: 1.5rem
  margin: 1rem 0

li
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem